## Description {#details}

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/json/objectkey">ObjectKey</a> is a used to capture keys in <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/json/object">Object</a>.

Like <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/json/value">Value</a> but:
<ul>
<li>only strings are allowed</li>
<li>it&#39;s optimized for the string literal case (Owned == nullptr) Like <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/json/value">Value</a>, strings must be UTF-8. See isUTF8 documentation for details.</li>
</ul>
